Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.46,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭一人之力解决了这么多虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:08.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个厉害角色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:09.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:40.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有能出战的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:51.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武家巡逻组 无法再继续履行职责了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾上大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给鄙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:04.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已夸下海口要守卫江户安全 却落此窝囊地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:19.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛 在你回来之前 我会让你看看武家组的强韧的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 要尽快前去增援
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【与父亲的修行！富岳三十六剑 ！！】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您快走吧 吉宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:45.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此等小事 何须如此惊慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:47.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉宗大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这只不过是个预告罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:59.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西边 还有一场恶战在等待着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:01.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万万不可啊 家重大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去援助我的挚友仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.43,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:14.04,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是家重大人 您有学过剑术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:14.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一窍不通！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连切水果都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未有过！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我有丰富的理论知识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:25.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说剑术原本发祥于名为东国七流的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:29.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由七名神官从东国中心发扬光大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:34.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要借这些知识 替那家伙守护住他的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仁兵卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.72,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:47.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救大姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:05.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常住战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春小姐 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫大人 我就知道您一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:18.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:32.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么庞大的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭一人之力解决了这么多虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个厉害角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭一人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:55.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来无恙啊 仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:09.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部空门正对敌人 你这个蠢儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:16.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行还远远不够  身为武士 应常住战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都要如身临战场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨遵父亲教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:27.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我来看看你长进了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.30,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:41.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为顺利完成八丈岛任务及成功守住江户 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:48.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也跟着沾光 真是惭愧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么呢 源十郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:55.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场祝捷大会能够召开 您可是功不可没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:06:02.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我是不想与身份低贱者对酌的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 源十郎大人当真好本领呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:10.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真教人甘拜下风  有机会请务必与在下切磋一番
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:14.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请也跟在下切磋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爹真有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟好久不见 没什么要讲的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:25.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必 我们已经用剑充分交谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么用剑交谈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你单方面被揍而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:34.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们平时就是那样交谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你家里…真够呛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 在八丈岛上到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:47.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很遗憾 几乎都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:49.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:02.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 关于仁兵卫君的变貌我们会调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心不要说漏了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.91,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下只记得跟虫狩打斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:15.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有跟虫奉行大人的侍女小姐相见的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍女小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 虫奉行大人现在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下有事一定要见他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你我的身份 怎么可能见得到她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见不到？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长福丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:41.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 我好想你?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户真是个好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫 你在这儿都学到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开家也有段时间了 说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一件重要的事就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识到了自己的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从来到江户
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:16.59,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因自己没出息 总是受助于他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:23.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在八丈岛也一定…吃了败战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:28.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身负保护虫奉行大人 守卫江户的重任…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 我辜负了您的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:34.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…就因为我的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:38.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给父亲开创的「月岛流」剑术抹了黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:43.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是 万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:50.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫啊 我可从来不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何时准许过你自称「月岛流」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有多少斤两我还不知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:03.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个半吊子 竟想着背负「月岛流」这个名号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子未免太猖狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:08.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天开始 踏上修行之路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛变化的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:25.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为把我的头发含于口中所致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:31.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 普通人是不可能发生如此变样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开门见山地说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:40.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和你一样是虫狩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没义务告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 请保重贵体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:53.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟现在的你手无缚鸡之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:13.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  此处竟是这等冷清之所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:18.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在月岛在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:38.72,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛 是你让我想起我也是人类之躯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:42.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却没能告诉你我的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还怀疑你是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:49.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我说一声对不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这愿望若能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:55.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕此后再也无法从那里出来也无悔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月 月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:14.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春小姐 多谢你送来的慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:15.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:26.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫大人 明天开始就要踏上修行之旅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是早点歇息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:33.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 为了江户 为了虫奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下一定要抓紧练习 让自己变强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳公公 早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:59.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这次修行 我一定要变强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游遍富士五湖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在富士树海收集食物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去攀登富士山的山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:19.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始 我要将月岛流的秘技传授于你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:24.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该…该不会是教我富岳三十六剑吧 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐天呐 终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 富岳三十六剑就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:37.91,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人年轻之时呕心沥血领悟出的三十六式刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:42.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中包括能一刀劈开大海的绝技
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抢你老爹的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:51.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期限是向松之原小鸟大人请的这三天假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:55.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这三天内你需将三十六招式全部学会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全…全部的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那个时候 仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:04.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以堂堂正正地使用月岛流的名号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:08.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:16.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:19.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你接下来要学的富岳招式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:30.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛流 富岳铁锤斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:36.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是砍 却如同锤击般独特的斩击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:39.80,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人的拿手绝招 富岳铁锤斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要涌上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲远点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:58.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 莫非您让富士山爆发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:06.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里使出富岳铁锤斩 以阻止富士山爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:09.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这里的岩石施加重击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所产生的压力可以阻止火山爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:19.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按这个速度 三天后岩浆就会溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:23.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 如果在那之前你还没学会铁锤斩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山脚下人们居住的村落就会被烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 这是不是有失妥当 父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:34.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我学会这个招式用了五年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.91,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今可没时间让你磨磨蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲大人 真是太伟大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:47.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人您特意为我创造苛刻的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:50.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了全面激发我的潜力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:57.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不会辜负您的期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富岳铁锤斩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心切开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:37.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:43.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整两天不眠不休 不吃不喝 修炼到倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.46,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子不愧是继承了你的血统啊 悟性极高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你唱唱叶的「摇篮曲」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:08.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵闻此为神中神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:15.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太秦打惩常世神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍睡了一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连标记的岩石都被淹没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你要怎么办呢 仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:40.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩浆可不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会大概还有一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失败了 山脚下的人们就会有性命之虞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:09.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的奥义都在父亲大人的教诲中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为武士 就该常住战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:15.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时何地都要如身临战场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出阵 月岛 仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:41.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要一击即中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后变得更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:52.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护江户民众
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:56.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了有一天能兑现那个诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛流 富岳铁锤斩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场的敌人 不仅是要砍倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要彻底打败他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:24.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了 终于完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看仔细了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:30.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:32.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富岳山岚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本应该是你接下来要学的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会尽快学会刚刚所见的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让刀法日渐精进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你就要踏上修行的旅途了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如早点歇息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:27.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 为了江户 为了虫奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下要抓紧时间练习 让自己变强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:35.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说因为身份和地位的悬殊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:38.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下与虫奉行大人 是不可能轻易相见的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:45.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让他人知道 我与月岛私下碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:49.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会给他带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:53.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份和地位都相差太悬殊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:59.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 总有一天在下会与虫奉行大人见面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变得更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:05.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为那个能够面见虫奉行大人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:11.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在下已经与侍女小姐约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:15.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要与大家一起仰望江户的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待着那一刻的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:04.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等神圣庄严的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德川幕府的蠢货们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:12.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的时代将在下一个冬天终结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿飞 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:22.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行所在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:01.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:04.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有人要来采访虫奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:08.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非再下也会被采访吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:13.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 虫奉行 全程展示！！大江户的女浴室！！
