Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:21.05,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:23.59,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了令人忧伤的纯粹简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:26.89,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在夕阳西下时的道场一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.67,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挥洒着汗水练习刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:33.08,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.64,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了引人发笑的满腔热情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.02,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「我也是有梦想的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:41.86,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像傻瓜般这样大声叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:46.27,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:49.17,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝阳东升的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:52.14,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你会在喧闹的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.04,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拼命奔跑着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.17,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:00.99,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}深夜降临的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.13,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你会穿过宽阔的大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.03,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在河滩边诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:09.71,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是这样吧 我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:16.58,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.23,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了一颗赤子之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:22.28,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你正守护着重要的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:25.43,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}脸上透露着决心吧
